<p>Context: <em>Merging</em> is participatory experience exploring the power of physical touch, co-created with <a href="https://austejaliu.com" target="_blank">Austeja Liupševičiūtė</a>.</p>

<p>My Role: concept, space-holding, facilitation</p>

<p>Magic: combining cacao and guided touch into a simple yet powerful experience.</p>

<blockquote>
  <p>“I’m very moved. There are tears that want to come out right now and it’s quite difficult for me to put words to this experience.”
– Marilou</p>
</blockquote>

<blockquote>
  <p>“I could feel so much love and tenderness and openness in the room… It was so beautiful. It’s very precious to be a part of it.”
– Silvia</p>
</blockquote>

<blockquote>
  <p>“I don’t know if my heart was as big before as I feel it now. I feel really connected to you… You are in me like little bubbles.”
– Hanna</p>
</blockquote>

